There is a C --> G polymorphism at base pair 215 in ORF (corresponding to codon 72- switching from a proline to an arginine). This base pair substitution was encoded in the insert in the pLenti6 plasmid obtained from Addgene and is a common sequence polymorphism observed in p53.
